videos.headline: Brandon Chapman hauls in a TD catch for Wake Forest
videos.description: Sam Hartman connects with Brandon Chapman on a 4-yard touchdown pass on the opening drive of the Gator Bowl.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Brandon Chapman hauls in a TD catch for Wake Forest) 2021/12/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Aaron Young rushes in for 12-yard TD
videos.description: Rutgers RB Aaron Young bounces off a block and runs in for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Aaron Young rushes in for 12-yard TD) 2021/12/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: A.T. Perry makes amazing catch for a 29-yard TD

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (A.T. Perry makes amazing catch for a 29-yard TD) 2021/12/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Clever reverse play gets Rutgers into red zone
videos.description: Rutgers WR Isaiah Washington throws the ball across the field to backup QB Johnny Langan, who breaks off a 26-yard play.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Clever reverse play gets Rutgers into red zone) 2021/12/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: This hurdle from A.T. Perry didn't count, but it was epic
videos.description: A.T. Perry flies over a Rutgers defender as he heads toward the end zone, but he had already stepped out of bounds.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (This hurdle from A.T. Perry didn't count, but it was epic) 2021/12/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Wake Forest's Ryan Smenda Jr. ejected for targeting
videos.description: Ryan Smenda Jr. is ejected from the Gator Bowl for a hit to the head against Rutgers QB Gavin Wimsatt.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Wake Forest's Ryan Smenda Jr. ejected for targeting) 2021/12/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Sam Hartman scrambles for 35 yards to set up a TD pass
videos.description: Sam Hartman somehow evades a sack and runs for a huge gain, then becomes the third QB in ACC history to reach 50 touchdowns in a season.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Sam Hartman scrambles for 35 yards to set up a TD pass) 2021/12/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Justice Ellison breaks off a 27-yard TD run for Wake Forest
videos.description: Justice Ellison fends off two Rutgers defenders as he races into the end zone on a 27-yard touchdown run.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Justice Ellison breaks off a 27-yard TD run for Wake Forest) 2021/12/31 ESHEET
